== UBUZIMA BWITE ==


'''Ishimwe Sandra Elyse''' ni umunyarwandakazi  afite imyaka 23 ubu aba muri mu Mujyi wa fonixe muri Arizona. Yavukiye mu [[akarere ka Nyaruguru]] aba ari naho akurira. Ni umwana wa kabiri mu muryango w’abana bane. Ubwo yari akiri muto, yabonye amahirwe yo kujya kwiga mu [[Ubushinwa|Bushinwa]] nyuma aza kuhava ajya kuba muri British Guiana mu [[Amerika y’Epfo|Amarika y'Epho]]. Nyuma yaje kujya muri [[Amerika ya Ruguru|Amerika]] muri Arizona ari naho aba kugeza ubu.

=== IBYO AKUNDA ===
'''Ishimwe Sandra Elyse''' Akunda gutembera, kunguka inshuti nshya, gusoma ibitabo no kuzamuka imisozi. Ubu ari kwiga ibijyanye no kumurika imideli no gukina filime muri [https://www.johncasablancastestimonials.com/ John Casablancas Modeling and Acting Agency]. Arimo no kwiga Icyiciro cya Kabiri cya kaminuza mu bijyanye n’Ubuzima. Uyu mukobwa avuga neza [[Ikinyarwanda]], Igishinwa, [[Icyongereza]] n’[[Igifaransa]].

