=== UMUSHINGA YARI AFITE ===
Uyu Ishimw kuba yahawe iri kamba bivuze ikintu gikomeye kuri we cyane ko rizamufasha mu bikorwa bye. Ati “Guhabwa iri kamba bivuze ikintu gikomeye kuko narariruhiye none birangiye ndibonye kandi kuba ari ikintu nzahorana bizamfasha. Bigiye bituma ntangira ibikorwa by’umushinga nari mfite.” Ibikorwa bye azabitangirira muri Arizona ariko arateganya kubigeza no mu Rwanda. Ati “Nintanabasha kuza mu Rwanda nzifashisha inzego zibishinzwe kugira ngo ibikorwa by’umushinga wanjye bigere ku bo byagenewe.” Sandra Elyse Ishimwe afite umushinga ugamije gufasha abategarugori 140 muri Amerika no mu Rwanda.



Mu minsi yashize yavuzeko ko uyu mushinga we waturutse ku buzima bugoye yanyuzemo ariko akaza gufashwa n’umutegarugori bataziranye. Uretse ibyo kandi hari ubuzima abari n’abategarugori banyuzemo mu bihe bikomeye bya COVID-19 ndetse n’ishyirwa mu bikorwa rya gahunda ya ‘Guma mu rugo’ yatangiye muri Werurwe 2020 ahenshi ku Isi, aho abenshi bakorewe ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina, abangavu benshi batewe inda zitateganyijwe, ingo nyinshi zihura n’ikibazo cy’inzara. 

Ibyo byamuteye gutangiza umushinga udaharanira inyungu witwa “The Ursula Women Foundation’’ uzita kandi ukanateza imbere abari n’abategarugori cyane cyane abagizweho n’ingaruka zaturutse kuri Covid-19. Avuga ko impamvu yahisemo izina ‘The Ursula Women Foundation ari uko “Ursula’’ ari izina ry’igisimba mu Kinyarwanda bakunze kwita “idubu”. Ni cyo cya mbere ku Isi kizwiho kuba ahantu hagoranye cyane mu rubura n’ubukonje bwinshi, ariko kikaba kihabaye ibinyejana n’ibinyejana kubera imwe mu myitwarire yacyo irimo kwemera cyangwa kwakira no kwihangana. Ati “Umutegarugori nawe namugereranyije n’iyo nyamaswa yiga kuba ahantu hagoye ariko ntibiyibuze kubaho. Na bo babaho mu buzima bugoye ariko bakabasha gutanga umusanzu ukomeye mu muryango; ni bo batwita amezi icyenda, bakabyara, bakagira uruhare mu mikurire y’umwana kuko aribo bamukurikirana umunsi ku wundi.” Umuryango The Ursula Women Foundation watangijwe n’uyu mukobwa urateganya guhindurira ubuzima abari n’abategarugori 70 bo mu Mujyi wa Phoenix muri Leta ya Arizona ndetse n’abagera kuri 70 bo mu Rwanda. Uzahera ku bafite imyaka 12 kuzamura mu gihe kingana n’umwaka umwe gusa, ndetse imibare ikazagenda yiyongera ubwo uzagenda wagura ibikorwa b yawo mu bihugu bitandukanye hirya no hino ku Isi.<ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/ishimwe-yahawe-ikamba-yari-yariganijwe-muri-miss-africa-arizona-2022</ref>

